quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,"Wallatee ahsanat farjahafanafakhna feeha min roohinawajaAAalnaha wabnaha ayatanlilAAalameen"
  21,92,"Inna hathihi ommatukum ommatan wahidatanwaana rabbukum faoAAbudoon"
  21,93,"WataqattaAAoo amrahum baynahum kullunilayna rajiAAoon"
  21,94,"Faman yaAAmal mina assalihatiwahuwa mu/minun fala kufrana lisaAAyihi wa-innalahu katiboon"
  21,95,"Waharamun AAalaqaryatin ahlaknaha annahum la yarjiAAoon"
  21,96,"Hatta itha futihatya/jooju wama/jooju wahum min kulli hadabin yansiloon"
  21,97,"Waqtaraba alwaAAdu alhaqqufa-itha hiya shakhisatun absaru allatheenakafaroo ya waylana qad kunna fee ghaflatinmin hatha bal kunna thalimeen"
  21,98,"Innakum wama taAAbudoona min dooniAllahi hasabu jahannama antum laha waridoon"
  21,99,"Law kana haola-i alihatanma waradooha wakullun feeha khalidoon"
  21,100,"Lahum feeha zafeerun wahum feehala yasmaAAoon"
  21,101,"Inna allatheena sabaqat lahum minnaalhusna ola-ika AAanha mubAAadoon"
